{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"178962-kee-ahaan-sunaliyai","title":"की अहाँ सुनलियै?","description":"ध्यानसँ सुनियौ आ तखन अहाँ पायब जे चिड़ैसभ लग कहय लेल बहुते किछु छै।\r\n","language":"Maithili","langCode":"mai","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Raghu Kumar"],"illustrators":["Rohan Chakravarty"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/178962-kee-ahaan-sunaliyai"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527532/size3/d554b58ed4a31df51c45cca2a90e4aa0.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527532/size6/d554b58ed4a31df51c45cca2a90e4aa0.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48672/size6/b3698f706f9c803fcf4d2e0f5f9586e9.jpg","text":"चिड़िया गप करैत आछि। आ ओ बड्ड गप करैत अछि।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48673/size6/8a73244d3b29823d2e143a4db793072f.jpg","text":"वाहहहहहह!  \nवाहहहहहह!\nब्राह्मिणी चील भुखाएल बच्चा जेकाँ कनैत\nरहैछ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48674/size6/cf154fbb215a78fc6c90932f787ed0bc.jpg","text":"फ़िह्वी! फ़िह्वी!\nभंगराज\nचिड़ै हँसैत-खेलाइत बच्चा जकाँ सीटी बजबैत\nरहैछ।\nफ़िह्वी! फ़िह्वी!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48675/size6/6329ebf6c490f7fa8c369e7294b62b2f.jpg","text":"हू हू हू हू! हू हू हू हू!\nहँसयबला परबा एना\nहँसैछ\nजेना ओकरा गुदगुदी लागि रहल\nहोय।\nहू हू हू हू!\nहू हू हू हू!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48676/size6/3f77ade24760c011959d50469c997d9d.jpg","text":"पुक! पुक! पुक!\nबसंता चिड़ैक आवाज, लोहा पिटबाक आवाज सन\nहोइछ।\nपुक! पुक! पुक!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48677/size6/da65a217af07bceb2e72ec35d1e7e644.jpg","text":"कें! फ़िह्वी! हू हू! पुक! ओ के छियै?\nओ रैकेटसन नाङरिबला ड्रोंगो चिड़ै छी, जे आन चिड़ैक नकल नीक जेना कऽ\nसकैछ।\nकें! फ़िह्वी! हू हू! पुक!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48904/size6/79ad59559f5d99de346d10332ee66be8.jpg","text":"हमसभ नहि बूझै छियै जे चिड़ै की कहि रहल अछि,\nमुदा ई बूझै छियै, जे के बाजि रहल अछि।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":117}}